.PP
This feature be available up in Postfix 2.2 n' later.
.PP
Time units: s (seconds), m (minutes), h (hours), d (days), w (weeks).
Da default time unit is s (seconds).
.SH append_at_myorigin (default: yes)
With locally submitted mail, append tha strang "@$myorigin" ta mail
