pattern is replaced
by its contents; a "type:table" lookup table is matched when a name
matches a lookup key (the lookup result is ignored).  Continue long
lines by startin tha next line wit whitespace. Right back up in yo muthafuckin ass. Specify "!pattern"
to exclude a name from tha list. Da form "!/file/name" is supported
only up in Postfix version 2.4 n' later.
.PP
This feature be available up in Postfix 2.2 n' later.
