to exclude a user name from tha list. Da form "!/file/name" is
supported only up in Postfix version 2.4 n' later.
.PP
This feature be available up in Postfix 2.2 n' later.
.SH authorized_submit_users (default: static:mah playas)
List of playas whoz ass is authorized ta submit mail wit tha \fBsendmail\fR(1)
