.SH authorized_verp_clients (default: $mynetworks)
What remote SMTP clients is allowed ta specify tha XVERP command.
This command requests dat mail be served up one recipient at a
time wit a per recipient return address.
.PP
By default, only trusted clients is allowed ta specify XVERP.
