Da \fInumber\fR must be up in tha range 0..1 inclusive. With
\fInumber\fR equal ta "1", a thugged-out destinationz delivery concurrency
is incremented by 1 afta each successful pseudo-cohort.
.br
.br
.PP
A pseudo-cohort is tha number of deliveries equal ta a thugged-out destination's
delivery concurrency.
.PP
Use \fItransport\fR_destination_concurrency_positive_feedback
