.PP
Use \fItransport\fR_minimum_delivery_slots ta specify a
transport-specific override, where \fItransport\fR is tha master.cf
name of tha message delivery transport.
.SH default_privs (default: no muthafucka)
Da default muthafuckin rights used by tha \fBlocal\fR(8) delivery agent fo' delivery
to external file or command. Y'all KNOW dat shit, muthafucka!  These muthafuckin rights is used when delivery
is axed from a \fBaliases\fR(5) file dat is owned by \fBroot\fR, or
