.SH reset_baller_alias (default: no)
Reset tha \fBlocal\fR(8) delivery agentz scam of tha baller-alias
attribute, when deliverin mail ta a cold-ass lil lil pimp alias dat do not have
its own balla alias.
.PP
This feature be available up in Postfix 2.8 n' later n' shit. With older
Postfix releases, tha behavior be as if dis parameta is set to
