This feature be available up in Postfix 2.5 n' later.
.SH smtp_never_send_ehlo (default: no)
Never bust EHLO all up in tha start of a SMTP session. I aint talkin' bout chicken n' gravy biatch. Right back up in yo muthafuckin ass. See also the
