turned off fo' tha straight-up original gangsta delivery attempt.
.PP
Specify 0 ta enable tha PIX firewall
"<CR><LF>.<CR><LF>" bug workaround upon the
first delivery attempt.
.SH smtp_pix_workaroundz (default: disable_esmtp, delay_dotcrlf)
A list dat specifies zero or mo' workaroundz fo' CISCO PIX
firewall bugs. These workaroundz is implemented by tha Postfix
SMTP client. Workaround names is separated by comma or space, and
are case insensitive.  This parameta settin can be overruled with
per-destination smtp_pix_workaround_maps settings.
.IP "\fBdelay_dotcrlf\fR
Insert a thugged-out delay before sending
".<CR><LF>" afta tha end of tha message content.  The
delay is subject ta tha smtp_pix_workaround_delay_time and
smtp_pix_workaround_threshold_time parameta settings.
.br
.IP "\fBdisable_esmtp\fR
Disable all extended SMTP commands:
send HELO instead of EHLO.
.br
.br
.PP
This feature be available up in Postfix 2.4 n' later n' shit. Da default
settings is backwardz compatible wit earlier Postfix versions.
.SH smtp_quit_timeout (default: 300s)
Da Postfix SMTP client time limit fo' bustin  tha QUIT command,
and fo' receivin tha remote SMTP server response.
.PP
Time units: s (seconds), m (minutes), h (hours), d (days), w (weeks).
Da default time unit is s (seconds).
.SH smtp_quote_rfc821_envelope (default: yes)
