.ft R
.PP
This feature be available up in Postfix 2.5 n' later.
.SH smtp_sasl_mechanism_filta (default: empty)
If non-empty, a Postfix SMTP client filta fo' tha remote SMTP
serverz list of offered SASL mechanisms.  Different client and
server implementations may support different mechanizzle lists; by
default, tha Postfix SMTP client will use tha intersection of the
