is ignored. Y'all KNOW dat shit, muthafucka! Specify "!pattern" ta exclude a mechanizzle name from the
list. Da form "!/file/name" is supported only up in Postfix version
2.4 n' later.
.PP
This feature be available up in Postfix 2.2 n' later.
.PP
