.SH smtp_sasl_tls_security_options (default: $smtp_sasl_security_options)
Da SASL authentication securitizzle options dat tha Postfix SMTP
client uses fo' TLS encrypted SMTP sessions.
.PP
This feature be available up in Postfix 2.2 n' later.
.SH smtp_sasl_tls_verified_security_options (default: $smtp_sasl_tls_security_options)
Da SASL authentication securitizzle options dat tha Postfix SMTP
client uses fo' TLS encrypted SMTP sessions wit a verified server
