Use tha smtpd_discard_ehlo_keyword_address_maps feature
to discard EHLO keywordz selectively.
.br
.SH smtpd_end_of_data_restrictions (default: empty)
Optionizzle access restrictions dat tha Postfix SMTP server
applies up in tha context of tha SMTP END-OF-DATA command.
See SMTPD_ACCESS_README, section "Delayed evaluation of SMTP access
restriction lists" fo' a gangbangin' finger-lickin' rap of evaluation context n' time.
