Da followin restrictions is specific ta tha domain name shiznit
received wit tha ETRN command.
.IP "\fBcheck_etrn_access \fItype:table\fR\fR"
Search tha specified access database fo' tha ETRN domain name
or its parent domains. Right back up in yo muthafuckin ass. See tha \fBaccess\fR(5) manual page fo' details.
.br
.br
.PP
Other restrictions dat is valid up in dis context:
.IP \(bu
Generic restrictions dat can be used
in any SMTP command context, busted lyrics bout under smtpd_client_restrictions.
.IP \(bu
SMTP command specific restrictions busted lyrics bout under
smtpd_client_restrictions n' smtpd_helo_restrictions.
