.fi
.ad
.ft R
.SH smtpd_expansion_filta (default: peep "postconf -d" output)
What charactas is allowed up in $name expansionz of RBL reply
templates. Charactas not up in tha allowed set is replaced by "_".
Use C like escapes ta specify special charactas like fuckin whitespace.
