it chizzlez under overload ta just 1. With Postfix 2.5 n' earlier,
the SMTP server always allows up ta 20 errors by default.
.SH smtpd_helo_required (default: no)
Require dat a remote SMTP client introduces itself wit tha HELO
or EHLO command before bustin  tha MAIL command or other commands
that require EHLO negotiation.
.PP
Example:
.PP
.nf
.na
.ft C
