.SH smtpd_proxy_filta (default: empty)
Da hostname n' TCP port of tha mail filterin proxy server.
Da proxy receives all mail from tha Postfix SMTP server, n' is
supposed ta give tha result ta another Postfix SMTP server process.
.PP
Specify "host:port" or "inet:host:port" fo' a TCP endpoint, or
