.PP
Da "inet:" n' "unix:" prefixes is available up in Postfix 2.3
and later.
.SH smtpd_proxy_options (default: empty)
List of options dat control how tha fuck tha Postfix SMTP server
communicates wit a funky-ass before-queue content filter n' shit. Right back up in yo muthafuckin ass. Specify zero or
more of tha following, separated by comma or whitespace.
.IP "\fBspeed_adjust\fR"
Do not connect ta a funky-ass before-queue content filta until a entire
