.PP
This feature be available up in Postfix 2.7 n' later.
.SH smtpd_proxy_timeout (default: 100s)
Da time limit fo' connectin ta a proxy filta n' fo' bustin  or
receivin shiznit. I aint talkin' bout chicken n' gravy biatch.  When a cold-ass lil connection fails tha client gets a
generic error message while mo' detailed shiznit is logged to
