Da default time unit is s (seconds).
.PP
This feature be available up in Postfix 2.1 n' later.
.SH smtpd_recipient_limit (default: 1000)
Da maximal number of recipients dat tha Postfix SMTP server
accepts per message delivery request.
.SH smtpd_recipient_overshoot_limit (default: 1000)
Da number of recipients dat a remote SMTP client can bust in
