is logged up in tha maillog file.
.br
.IP "\fBclient_port\fR"
Da client TCP port dat is
logged up in tha maillog file.
.br
.IP "\fBlocaltime\fR"
Da server local time (Mmm dd
hh:mm:ss) dat is logged up in tha maillog file.
.br
.IP "\fBserver_name\fR"
