(like behind a load-balancer), where tha server name can help
the server support crew ta quickly find tha right log files.
.br
.br
.PP
Notes:
.IP \(bu
NOT SUPPORTED is other attributes like fuckin sender, recipient,
or main.cf parameters.
.IP \(bu
For safety reasons, text dat do not match
$smtpd_expansion_filta is censored.
.br
.PP
This feature supports tha two-characta sequence \en as a request
for a line break up in tha foota text. Postfix automatically inserts
afta each line break tha three-digit SMTP reply code (and optional
