permission rulez is preferably implemented wit smtpd_relay_restrictions,
so dat a permissive spam blockin policy under
smtpd_recipient_restrictions will no longer result up in a permissive
mail relay policy.
.PP
For backwardz compatibility, cribs dat migrate from Postfix
