contents; a "type:table" lookup table is matched when a table entry
matches a lookup strang (the lookup result is ignored).  Continue
long lines by startin tha next line wit whitespace. Right back up in yo muthafuckin ass. Specify
"!pattern" ta exclude a address or network block from tha list.
Da form "!/file/name" is supported only up in Postfix version 2.4 and
later.
