.PP
Specify a list of restrictions, separated by commas and/or whitespace.
Continue long lines by startin tha next line wit whitespace.
Restrictions is applied up in tha order as specified; tha first
restriction dat matches wins.
.PP
Da followin restrictions is specific ta tha sender address
received wit tha MAIL FROM command.
.IP "\fBcheck_sender_access \fItype:table\fR\fR"
Search tha specified \fBaccess\fR(5) database fo' tha MAIL FROM
address, domain, parent domains, or localpart@, n' execute the
correspondin action.
