.IP "\fBreject_authenticated_sender_login_mismatch\fR"
Enforces tha reject_sender_login_mismatch restriction for
authenticated clients only. This feature be available in
Postfix version 2.1 n' later.
.br
.IP "\fBreject_non_fqdn_sender\fR"
