The
unverified_sender_reject_code parameta specifies tha numerical
response code when a address is known ta bounce (default: 450,
change tha fuck into 550 when yo ass is Kool & Tha Gang dat it is safe ta do so).
.br
Da unverified_sender_defer_code specifies tha numerical response
code when a address address probe failed cuz of a temporary problem
(default: 450).
.br
Da unverified_sender_tempfail_action parameter
specifies tha action afta address probe failure cuz of a temporary
problem (default: defer_if_permit).
.br
This feature be available
in Postfix 2.1 n' later.
