This is da most thugged-out appropriate settin fo' hood MX hosts, n' be always
used wit opportunistic TLS encryption. I aint talkin' bout chicken n' gravy biatch. Da underlyin cipherlist
is specified via tha tls_export_cipherlist configuration parameter,
which yo ass is straight fuckin encouraged ta not chizzle.
.br
.IP "\fBlow\fR"
